result.name: AJISEN RAMEN

reviews.text:
Great food and great staff. Family oriented. Always well treated by the staff. Honest price. Fresh food, fresh ingredients. I am always impressed in how the staff is always trying to make we feel good.

Strongly Recommend! One of our favorites!

Good ramen and what you expect from a chain store. The ramen came promptly by uninterested and unmotivated staff, a common sight in HK. The manager (and the one who seemed like it) was more friendly, but the other staff were clearly disinterested. Location is good too as it's right across the street from Tung Chung MTR. Overall go if you're craving noodles but don't expect anything special.
Service is good. Food portion is small for the price

Great ramen for a great price. Students get a discount as well so it's a good place for students. Also every 22nd of the month they serve ramen for $22 hkd which is a massive bargain for what you get.
Good ramen for the price prompt service.
